OL,3,CBritish woman becomes 13th person to
OL,4,Cdie in Spanish wildfires
OL,6,FA 93-year-old British woman has died
OL,7,Fafter being injured in the fierce
OL,8,Fwildfires that swept through southern
OL,9,FSpain, authorities said.
OL,11,FThe Andalusian government said the
OL,12,Fwoman was taken to hospital on Friday
OL,13,Fafter suffering burns to about 20% of
OL,14,Fher body.
OL,16,FHer death was confirmed on Sunday
OL,17,Fafternoon, bringing the total number
OL,18,Fof fatalities from the fires to 13.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
