OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783952425
OL,3,CBritish woman becomes 13th person to
OL,4,Cdie in Spanish wildfires
OL,6,FFour other Britons are believed to
OL,7,Fhave died while trying to escape the
OL,8,Ffires on Friday.
OL,10,FLast week, four bodies were found near
OL,11,Fthe village of Bedar, in a burned-out
OL,12,Fcar with its steering wheel on the
OL,13,Fright, leading authorities to believe
OL,14,Fthey were of "British origin".
OL,16,FOn Sunday, two British hikers were
OL,17,Ffound alive but badly burned.
