OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783952425
OL,3,CBritish woman becomes 13th person to
OL,4,Cdie in Spanish wildfires
OL,6,FThe man and woman, who have not been
OL,7,Fidentified, are thought to have
OL,8,Fsuffered 40% burns, according to the
OL,9,FSpanish national broadcaster, RTVE.
OL,11,FThe pair was discovered by a team of
OL,12,FCivil Guards, who said they had
OL,13,Falready checked the area but had a
OL,14,Ffeeling that they should return.
OL,16,FIn an interview with RTVE, the Civil
OL,17,FGuard officers said they found the two
OL,18,FBritish people alive just as night was
OL,19,Ffalling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
