FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783952425
OL,3,CBritish woman becomes 13th person to
OL,4,Cdie in Spanish wildfires
OL,6,FSergeant Pedro Barre told the
OL,7,Fbroadcaster: "That experience we
OL,8,Faccumulate over the years is what
OL,9,Ftells you: take another look, give it
OL,10,Fone last try, check again just in
OL,11,Fcase."
OL,13,FHe said they called out and used
OL,14,Fwhistles, before eventually hearing a
OL,15,Fsound which they thought at first
OL,16,Fcould have been an echo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
