OL,3,CBritish woman becomes 13th person to
OL,4,Cdie in Spanish wildfires
OL,6,FSpanish authorities believe all the
OL,7,Fvictims were foreign tourists, who are
OL,8,Fthought to have attempted to escape on
OL,9,Ffoot after apparently abandoning their
OL,10,Fvehicles and trying to flee through
OL,11,Frugged terrain.
OL,13,FSubscribe for to our weekly newsletter
OL,14,Ffor exclusive and original coverage
OL,15,Ffrom ITV News. Direct to your inbox
OL,16,Fevery Friday morning.
