OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1783952425
OL,3,CBritish woman becomes 13th person to
OL,4,Cdie in Spanish wildfires
OL,6,FAntonio Sanz, head of Andalusia's
OL,7,Femergency services, previously said
OL,8,Fthat authorities had completed post-
OL,9,Fmortem examinations and DNA samples
OL,10,Fwere collected to identify them.
OL,12,FSpain has suffered frequent and severe
OL,13,Fheatwaves in recent years, with
OL,14,Ftemperatures often exceeding 40C.
OL,16,FIn June, Spain experienced several
OL,17,Fdays of record-setting heat, with more
OL,18,Fthan 1,000 excess deaths attributed to
OL,19,Fheat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
